data.title: Atul’s Song A Day- A choice collection of Hindi Film & Non-Film Songs
data.meta_description: Posts about Anmol Ghadi written by Atul
data.meta_site_name: Atul’s Song A Day-   A choice collection of  Hindi Film & Non-Film Songs
data.text:
This blog discusses Bollywood songs of yesteryears. Every song has a brief description, followed by a video link, and complete lyrics of the song.

This is a labour of love, where “new” songs are added every day, and that has been the case for over SIXTEEN years. This blog has over 18400 song posts by now.

This blog is active and online for over 5000 days since its beginning on 19 july 2008.
